#. Plugin Name of the plugin/theme
msgid "Wbcom Designs - BuddyPress Member Reviews"
msgstr "Wbcom Designs - BuddyPress Mitgliederbewertungen"

#. Plugin URI of the plugin/theme
msgid "https://wbcomdesigns.com/downloads/buddypress-user-profile-reviews/"
msgstr "https://wbcomdesigns.com/downloads/buddypress-user-profile-reviews/"

#. Description of the plugin/theme
msgid ""
"Enhances the BuddyPress community by allowing registered users to post "
"reviews on other members' profiles. This feature is exclusive to registered "
"members, ensuring unbiased feedback by preventing users from reviewing their "
"own profiles."
msgstr ""
"Erweitert die BuddyPress-Community, indem es registrierten Nutzern "
"ermöglicht, Bewertungen zu den Profilen anderer Mitglieder abzugeben. Diese "
"Funktion ist exklusiv für registrierte Mitglieder, um unvoreingenommenes "
"Feedback zu gewährleisten, indem Benutzer daran gehindert werden, ihre "
"eigenen Profile zu bewerten."

#. Author of the plugin/theme
msgid "Wbcom Designs"
msgstr "Wbcom Designs"

#. Author URI of the plugin/theme
msgid "https://wbcomdesigns.com"
msgstr "https://wbcomdesigns.com/plugins"
